Running this query which is supposed to materialize all properties across all graphs causes an error upon restarting the server:
Sparql
Insert {
  Graph ?g { ?p a <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> }
}
{
  { Select Distinct ?g ?p {
    Graph ?g {
      ?s ?p ?o
    } } }
}
;

14:24:21 OpenLink Virtuoso Universal Server
14:24:21 Version 07.20.3214-pthreads for Linux as of Aug 31 2015
14:24:21 uses parts of OpenSSL, PCRE, Html Tidy
